### Weaviate | 🦜️🔗 Langchain

Weaviate is an open source vector database that stores both objects and vectors, allowing for combining vector search with structured filtering. LangChain connects to Weaviate via the weaviate-ts-client package, the official Typescript client for...

This is the import you need:

`import { WeaviateStore } from "langchain/vectorstores/weaviate";`

